summary: I really love how this era Taylor has put so much effort into meeting us, bonding with us, she randomly appears on Instagram and...
body:
I really love how this era Taylor has put so much effort into meeting us, bonding with us, she randomly appears on Instagram and tumblr and likes posts, she pops up on swifties’ livestreams, the secret session, the rep room, everything. This really shows how much she loves and appreciates us, no need to mention that she always thanks us for attending her concerts and fully being there, dancing and screaming her lyrics. She loves us just as much as we love her and we have such a beautiful relationship with her I’m sobbing😭 Not many other celebrities go this far to meet their fans and talk to them for even a few minutes, that’s why I love Taylor so much. She actually cares.

@taylorswift @taylornation
